<bibRefCitation id="EFD24B053665FFAA2A29FBADFD1C94B9" author="PACE R" box="[576,693,1147,1169]" pageId="2" pageNumber="209" pagination="155 - 192" refId="ref22540" refString="PACE R. (2011): Biodiversita delle Aleocharinae della Cina: Athetini, prima parte, generi Lasiosomina, Hydrosmecta, Amischa, Alomaina, Paraloconota, Bellatheta, Nepalota, Pelioptera, Tropimenelytron, Berca e Amphibolusa (Coleoptera, Staphylinidae). - Beitrage zur Entomologie, Keltern 61 (1), 155 - 192." type="journal article" year="2011">PACE 2011</bibRefCitation>
